  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>macaroni </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to a boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> cooked macaroni</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your<strong> cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p><p>Melt 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [40g]</span><span class=\"text-purple\"> </span><strong>butter</strong> in a pot over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add 20g<span class=\"text-purple\"> [30g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and stir with a wooden spoon for 1 min or until a sandy paste forms – this is your <strong>roux</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Gradually whisk the <strong>creamy stock</strong> into the roux, a little at a time, and cook for 5-6 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p><p>Once you have a thick sauce, stir through your<strong> Dijon mustard </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheddar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) then season with a good grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>béchamel sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your<strong> garlic </strong>and add it to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your<strong> basil</strong>,<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong>,<strong> </strong>3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong>, <strong>blanched peas </strong>and the juice of half your<strong> lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and semi-smooth – this is your <strong>pea pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheddar</strong> to a small bowl with a grind of <strong>pepper </strong>– these are your <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained macaroni</strong> to the béchamel sauce – this is your <strong>pasta mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> pasta mixture </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Mix through the <strong>pea pesto </strong>then top with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until it's golden – this is your <strong>mac 'n' peas</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>to a bowl with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your<strong> zingy salad</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/mac-n-peas-with-zingy-salad/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>mac 'n' peas </strong>with the <strong>zingy salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
